rnered the highest number of comments. Therefore, we encourage the media to play a more proactive role in reinforcing positive conservation messaging by presenting the myriad ways in which bats contribute to safeguarding human well-being and ecosystem functioning.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "L\u00f3pez-Baucells, Adri\u00e0", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Revilla-Mart\u00edn, Natalia", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Mas, Maria", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Alonso-Alonso, Pedro", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Budinski, Ivana", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Fraixedas, Sara", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Fern\u00e1ndez-Llamazares, \u00c1lvaro", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["COVID-19", "Chiroptera", "Disease", "Risk perception", "Science communication", "Social media", "Virus", "Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/590e62f96ff8ca66e6597de1775760d7", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/678dab54a961003fcf4f42d705b177592806bf67e5aee15d8b3639228b34e8a6", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/ZB6KWUE7", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/ZB6KWUE7", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/040cd54e85b0e62c1ec0218efcd7ff9c!/b89136-91626", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journ